In addition to the LGPL license text, the following exclusions and clarifications to the LGPL conditions apply to Duke:
   1. Making modifications to Duke configuration files, build scripts and configuration headers in order to create a customised build setup of Duke with the otherwise unmodified source code, does not constitute a derived work.
